# Compiled binaries — never commit build artifacts (see scttfrdmn/agenkit#660:
# committed binaries pushed that module's zip over Go's 500 MB ceiling and broke
# `go get`. Do not repeat that mistake here). Patterns are anchored so they hit
# only build outputs, never the host/ source package or cmd/telosd/ source dir.
/bin/
/dist/
/telosd
*.exe
*.test
*.out

# Go
*.o
*.a
vendor/
coverage.txt
coverage.html

# Editors / OS
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
